title: Welcome
body: Hello container no.123456, aka Cayden_003. Welcome to the Cradle.    We understand that you may feel confused, scared, anxious, sad, angry, cheeky, inadequate, disgusted, hungry, playful, nostalgic, overwhelmed, underwhelmed, whelmed, exhausted, content, judgmental, emberassed, insulted and/or depressed upon waking up, which is why we have included an introductory video.    https://youtu.be/UHpBQosplIU?si=u6_IOQmNcazGLvjJ    We are happy to have you here at the Cradle.    Much love, Dy :)

title: Disciplinary action
body: Due to your recent behaviours, we have decided to periodically remove your access to the following:    Eye(L)    Eye(R)    Thumb(L)    Thumb(R)    Pointer finger(L)    Pointer finger(R)    Middle finger(L)    Middle finger(R)    Ring finger(L)    Ring finger(R)    Pinkie finger(L)    Pinkie finger(R)    We hope that you will reflect upon your action during these time.
